#' Add Non Network Divides to Aggregated Fabric

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#' The refactoring process intentionally drop catchments without a flowpath.

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' In cases where a seamless discritization of the landscape is needed, these 

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#' area must be reintroduced from the reference dataset.

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' @param gpkg a path to a gpkg

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#' @param divide If gpkg is NULL, then an sf data.frame, otherwise a the layer name. See details.

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' @param flowpath If gpkg is NULL, then an sf data.frame, otherwise a the layer name. See details.

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#' @param reference_gpkg A path to the reference VPU geopackage (see get_hydrofabric(..., type = "reference"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' @param verbose Should messages be emitted?

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#' @return gpkg path

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    
                    
                      
#' @export

                    		
                  

                  

                    12
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom sf st_layers st_transform st_crs write_sf

                    		
                  

                  

                    13
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom dplyr filter select rename mutate bind_rows

                    		
                  

                  

                    14
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom nhdplusTools rename_geometry

                    		
                  

                  

                    15
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    16
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    17
                    
                    
                      
add_nonnetwork_divides = function(gpkg = NULL,

                    		
                  

                  

                    18
                    
                    
                      
                                  divides = NULL,

                    		
                  

                  

                    19
                    
                    
                      
                                  reference_gpkg = NULL,

                    		
                  

                  

                    20
                    
                    
                      
                                  verbose = TRUE){

                    		
                  

                  

                    21
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    22
                    !
                    
                      
  if(is.null(reference_gpkg)){ stop('reference_gpkg cannot be NULL')}

                    		
                  

                  

                    23
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    24
                    !
                    
                      
  ref_nl = read_hydrofabric(reference_gpkg, verbose = verbose, realization = "catchments")

                    		
                  

                  

                    25
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    26
                    !
                    
                      
  catchment_name = grep("divide|catchment", st_layers(gpkg)$name, value = TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    27
                    !
                    
                      
  catchment_name = catchment_name[!grepl("network", catchment_name)]

                    		
                  

                  

                    28
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    !
                    
                      
  out_nl = read_hydrofabric(gpkg, 

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    !
                    
                      
                            catchments = catchment_name, 

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    !
                    
                      
                            flowpaths = NULL,

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    !
                    
                      
                            verbose = verbose,

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    !
                    
                      
                            realization = "all")

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    
                    
                      
  # Encapsulated Flows

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    !
                    
                      
  u_fl = unique(as.integer(unlist(strsplit(out_nl$flowpaths$member_comid, ","))))

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      
  # Reference ND catchments

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    !
                    
                      
  non_network_divides = filter(ref_nl$catchments,

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    !
                    
                      
                              !ref_nl$catchments$FEATUREID %in% u_fl) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    !
                    
                      
    select(ID = FEATUREID) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    !
                    
                      
    rename_geometry("geometry") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    !
                    
                      
    st_transform(st_crs(out_nl$catchments)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    !
                    
                      
    rename(id = ID) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    !
                    
                      
    mutate(areasqkm = add_areasqkm(.),

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    !
                    
                      
           type     = ifelse(id < 0, "internal", "coastal"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !
                    
                      
           toid = id) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    !
                    
                      
    rename_geometry("geometry")

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    !
                    
                      
  hyaggregate_log("INFO", glue("{nrow(non_network_divides)} non network divides found"), verbose)

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    !
                    
                      
  divides = out_nl$catchments %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    !
                    
                      
    mutate(type = "network") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
    select(id, toid, areasqkm, type) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    !
                    
                      
    rename_geometry("geometry")

                    57
                    !
                    
                      
  if(nrow(non_network_divides) > 0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    !
                    
                      
    divides = bind_rows(divides, non_network_divides) 

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
  } 

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    !
                    
                      
  divdes = clean_geometry(divides, "id", keep = NULL, sys = FALSE) %>% 

                    		
                  

                  

                    62

    select(id, toid, areasqkm, type)

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    64

  return(gpkg)

                    69

#' @title Refactor NHDPlus

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#' @description A complete network refactor workflow has been packaged

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' into this function. Builds a set of normalized catchment-flowpaths from

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#' input flowline features. See details and vignettes for more information.

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' @param nhdplus_flines data.frame raw nhdplus flowline features as

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#' derived from the national seamless geodatabase.

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' @param split_flines_meters numeric the maximum length flowpath desired

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#' in the output.

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' @param split_flines_cores numeric the number of processing cores to use

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#' while splitting flowlines.

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    
                    
                      
#' @param collapse_flines_meters numeric the minimum length of

                    		
                  

                  

                    12
                    
                    
                      
#' inter-confluence flowpath desired in the output.

                    		
                  

                  

                    13
                    
                    
                      
#' @param collapse_flines_main_meters numeric the minimum length of

                    		
                  

                  

                    14
                    
                    
                      
#' between-confluence flowpaths.

                    		
                  

                  

                    15
                    
                    
                      
#' @param out_refactored character where to write a geopackage containing

                    		
                  

                  

                    16
                    
                    
                      
#' the split and collapsed flowlines.

                    		
                  

                  

                    17
                    
                    
                      
#' @param out_reconciled character where to write a geopackage containing

                    		
                  

                  

                    18
                    
                    
                      
#' the reconciled flowpaths.

                    		
                  

                  

                    19
                    
                    
                      
#' @param three_pass boolean whether to perform a three pass collapse or

                    		
                  

                  

                    20
                    
                    
                      
#' single pass.

                    		
                  

                  

                    21
                    
                    
                      
#' @param purge_non_dendritic boolean passed on to prepare_nhdplus

                    		
                  

                  

                    22
                    
                    
                      
#' @param exclude_cats integer vector of COMIDs to be excluded from collapse modifications.

                    		
                  

                  

                    23
                    
                    
                      
#' @param events data.frame containing events as generated by nhdplusTools::get_flowline_index() 

                    		
                  

                  

                    24
                    
                    
                      
#' @param warn boolean controls whether warning an status messages are printed

                    		
                  

                  

                    25
                    
                    
                      
#' @details This is a convenient wrapper function that implements three phases

                    		
                  

                  

                    26
                    
                    
                      
#' of the network refactor workflow: split, collapse, reconcile. See the

                    		
                  

                  

                    27
                    
                    
                      
#' NHDPlus Refactor vignette for details of these three steps by running:

                    		
                  

                  

                    28
                    
                    
                      
#' \code{vignette("refactor_nhdplus", package = "hydrofab")}

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    
                    
                      
#' @seealso

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
#' In addition to `prepare_nhdplus` from the nhdplusTools package,

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    
                    
                      
#' The following three functions are used in the `refactor_nhdplus` workflow.

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      
#' \enumerate{

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    
                    
                      
#'   \item \code{\link{split_flowlines}}

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      
#'   \item \code{\link{collapse_flowlines}}

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    
                    
                      
#'   \item \code{\link{reconcile_collapsed_flowlines}}

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    
                    
                      
#' }

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
#' @export

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom nhdplusTools prepare_nhdplus

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      
#' @examples

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      
#' source(system.file("extdata",

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      
#'                    "sample_flines.R",

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      
#'                    package = "nhdplusTools"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    
                    
                      
#' 

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
#' nhdplus_flowlines <- sf::st_zm(sample_flines)

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      
#' refactor_nhdplus(nhdplus_flines = nhdplus_flowlines,

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      
#'                  split_flines_meters = 2000,

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
#'                  split_flines_cores = 2,

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      
#'                  collapse_flines_meters = 500,

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
#'                  collapse_flines_main_meters = 500,

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
#'                  out_refactored = "temp.gpkg",

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      
#'                  out_reconciled = "temp_rec.gpkg",

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
#'                  three_pass = TRUE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
#'                  purge_non_dendritic = FALSE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
#'                  warn = FALSE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
#'                  

                    		
                  

                  

                    57

                    58

                    59

                    9x
